    },
    "语音模型将用于合成语音。选择 Siri 模型可使用本地合成，而选择大模型合成将通过 API 请求生成语音，后者需要配置有效的 API Key。" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Speech models will be used to synthesize speech. Selecting the Siri model will use native synthesis, while selecting Large Model Synthesis will generate speech via API requests, the latter requiring a valid API Key to be configured."
          }
        },
        "he" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
